body:
ToSKBitmap() causes artifacts and displays at the incorrect size in Windows Forms.

I'm able to generate the correct bitmaps with my own method below:

```
        public static SKBitmap BitmapToSKBitmap(Bitmap bitmap)
        {
            var info = new SKImageInfo(bitmap.Width, bitmap.Height);
            var skiaBitmap = new SKBitmap(info);

            for (int i = 0; i < bitmap.Width; i++)
            {
                for (int j = 0; j < bitmap.Height; j++)
                {
                    Color color = bitmap.GetPixel(i, j);
                    skiaBitmap.SetPixel(i, j, new SKColor(color.R, color.G, color.B, color.A));
                }
            }

            return skiaBitmap;
        }
```

